Revision history for Perl extension DateTime::LeapSecond.

0.03
      deprecates the stand-alone distribution.
      This module is now distributed with "DateTime".
      small POD fix - there is no defined 'precision'.

0.02  Fork to DateTime::LeapSecond
      Uses rd instead of system epoch
      New API: leap_seconds( $rd ), extra_seconds( $rd )

0.01  Wed May 29 14:15:00 2002
      - original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
          -X -n Date::Leapsecond

